A towering fortress made of sleek blue metallic server racks standing firm on a rocky cliff, while across a misty chasm sits a crumbling castle of gray stone with scattered bricks falling into the void below. The blue fortress has multiple interconnected towers with glowing data streams flowing between them, while the gray castle appears patched together with exposed wiring and scaffolding. Storm clouds gather over the gray castle while rays of sunlight break through onto the blue fortress. Rendered in a detailed comic book style with bold outlines, dramatic shading, and dynamic perspective looking up at both structures from the chasm below. Rich saturated colors with deep blues and teals contrasting against muted grays and browns.
